ND--><br><br>Exactly.  Doesn't affect rogues.<br><br>Not saying every last scrap of information on this board has to be rogue specific, BUT, the perception that this is somehow now a &quot;general Everquest info&quot; site is wrong and needs to be taken down a notch.  It isn't.  It was never intended to be.  It's a rogue board.<br><br>It's not a:<br><br>Bard board<br>Beastlord board<br>Cleric board<br>Druid board<br>Paladin board<br>Shadowknight board<br>Shaman board<br>Wizard board<br>Enchanter board<br>Necromancer board<br>Magician board<br>Ranger board<br><br>It's a Rogue board.  Members of other classes are always welcome here, that's true.  But the reason they are welcome is to discuss issues that involve and directly affect rogues, not to come here with druid/necro/magician/ranger etc... issues.<br><br>Yes, I play some alts (not twinks, but alternate chars) - a cleric, a monk, a shadowknight and a necromancer.  Know what? <br><br>When I wanted to know about different heals to use in different situations, I visited EQ Clerics and asked their advice.<br><br>When I wanted to know about the damage/delay of my monk's fists, I went to Monkly Business and found the information.<br><br>Those are the places for those discussions.  The Safehouse isn't.  The Safehouse is for when I want to research, ask questions and discuss issues pertinent to my Rogue. <p><font size=4><font face=hanzel, verdana, arial black><b>Kuurus</font></b><BR><font size=2><font face=hanzel, verdana, arial black>Assassin and Guild Leader</font><BR><font size=2><font face=hanzel, verdana, arial black><i>Retired</font></i><BR><font size=2><font face=andy, hanzel, arial black><b><A HREF=http://pub52.ezboard.com/bwarcry97210>Cry of War</A></font></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uinkiewiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Inkiewiz</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="ht